accessibility.text: Zidian outperforms Myrocks (Facebook) and CockroachDB (Baidu) on each and every of the TPC-H bechmark query on 10GB data;
On average is 33.5X and 20.5X faster than Cockr. and Myrocks, up to 1.3×103 and 1.5×104, respectively.
